## Implementation Steps

1. Copy these diagrams to their respective files
2. Create any missing files mentioned in the paths
3. Customize the content to match your specific analysis and data
4. Preview each diagram to ensure it renders correctly

## Tips for Creating Your Own Mermaid Diagrams

1. Use the [Mermaid Live Editor](https://mermaid.live/) to prototype diagrams
2. Reference the [Mermaid Syntax Documentation](https://mermaid.js.org/syntax/flowchart.html) for guidance
3. Keep diagrams focused on a single concept
4. Use consistent colors and styles across related diagrams
5. Consider creating a template file with commonly used diagram structures